detained by soldiers in the capital Kinshasa late this morning.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, Zairian rebels today entered the country's "economic
lung" and the second largest city Lubumbashi in the mineral-rich
province of Shaba in the southeast, after a fierce battle with the
elite units of the Zairian army.
</P>
<P>
