<P>
Gabriel added that during the seminar, many French businessmen
showed interests in increasing their investment in Angola, but he
stressed that this depends on the consolidation of peace in the
country and the clearance of land-mines from areas with potential
for industrial development.
</P>
<P>
He said that at present, French investors are most interested
in investing in Angola's maintenance work, match, food and light
industry, bread and other sectors. 
</P>
</TEXT>
