will increase mutual understanding and bilateral cooperation. He
pointed out that Syria was one of the earliest Arab states to
establish diplomatic relations with China. Since those began over
40 years ago, both countries have expanded cooperation, and the
future for cooperation is good.
</P>
<P>
China and Syria have similar views on major international
issues and support each other in international affairs, he said,
and that with the new situation of multipolarization, friendly
Sino-Syrian relations will increase, based on mutual respect,
equality and mutual benefit.
</P>
<P>
