He briefed Premier Li on the Mideast situation, and Li said
that the Chinese government and people are concerned about the
Mideast situation and firmly support the Mideast peace process.
</P>
<P>
Khaddam said that Syria and China have a long history of
friendly relations and that Syria hopes to increase ties with
China.
</P>
