<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, April 10 (Xinhua) -- The Organization of African
Unity (OAU) welcomed the direct negotiations held in South Africa
between the government of Zaire and the rebel Alliance of
Democratic Forces for the Liberation of Congo-Zaire.
</P>
