to reach an agreement on cessation of hostilities and to promote
a lasting solution to the crisis in that country.
</P>
<P>
He said he was encouraged by the support of both parties for
the U.N.-OAU peace plan.
</P>
<P>
Salim emphasized that OAU will continue to encourage the two
parties in their efforts to find a speedy and peaceful solution
to the conflict. 
