margin this year, and some will involve an investment of more than
10 billion yuan each. Among them are construction of a gas field,
synthetic ammonia and urea plants costing a total of 19 billion
yuan, a pulp mill involving a total investment of at 18.5 billion
yuan, and a nylon mill which will require eight billion yuan in
investment.  
