construction site, sent flames shooting 30 meters into the air
before it was brought under control quickly by firemen, the agency
quoted a police spokesman as saying.
</P>
<P>
Traffic near the scene snarled for hours and nearby residents
were evacuated after the blast.
</P>
<P>
The police were investigating the cause of the explosion, the
report said. 
