<HEADLINE> NZ Stocks Finish Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, April 10 (Xinhua) -- The New Zealand sharemarket
rose today in mostly lackluster and quiet trading.
</P>
<P>
The NZSE40 index ended 13 points higher at 2234 with a turnover
 of 42 million NZ dollars (29 million US dollars).
</P>
<P>
