from the private sector and donor community.
</P>
<P>
The two-day meeting, which is hosted by the Asian Development
Bank (ADB), will be dominated by discussions on resource
mobilization, partnership and cooperation between GMS governments
and the business sector and donor community.
</P>
<P>
